7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Activepieces and Parabola share a solid foundation of core features including Visual Builder, Api Connections, Scheduling, Conditional Logic. Where Activepieces pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Code Support, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Activepieces holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 8/10, while Parabola scores 7/10 overall and 8/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
8:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, both Activepieces and Parabola offer flexible pricing models. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Activepieces's free tier and Parabola's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
